entry.title: Some private schools facing 'survival issues' due to pandemic

media:group.media:title: Some private schools facing 'survival issues' due to pandemic
media:group.media:description: Some private schools are having "survival issues" due to the economic impact of the COVID-19 pandemic with parents losing jobs and overseas workers returning home, the Catholic Educational Association of the Philippines (CEAP) said Friday.

entry.title: LPA off Luzon now tropical depression Julian: PAGASA

media:group.media:title: LPA off Luzon now tropical depression Julian: PAGASA
media:group.media:description: A low pressure area off Luzon intensified into tropical depression Julian on Friday morning, while winds from the southwest threatened to bring rains over some parts of the country, the state weather bureau said.
